---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';

const lastUpdated = 'July 15, 2026';
---

<Layout title="Accessibility Statement" description="mikemurphy.ai's commitment to digital accessibility." canonical="/accessibility-statement/">
  <main class="mm-container py-16">
    <p class="mm-eyebrow">Legal</p>
    <h1 class="mm-h1 mt-3">Accessibility Statement</h1>
    <p class="mm-lede mt-5">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>

    <div class="mm-prose prose mt-8 max-w-3xl">
      <p>
        mikemurphy.ai is committed to making this Site accessible to as many
        people as possible, including people with disabilities. We are
        continually working to improve the accessibility and usability of the
        Site.
      </p>

      <h2>Our Standard</h2>
      <p>
        We aim to meet the Web Content Accessibility Guidelines (WCAG) 2.1
        Level AA. These guidelines explain how to make web content more
        accessible to people with a wide range of disabilities, including
        visual, auditory, physical, speech, cognitive, and neurological
        disabilities.
      </p>

      <h2>Measures We Take</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Using semantic HTML and clear heading structure</li>
        <li>Providing sufficient color contrast between text and backgrounds</li>
        <li>Ensuring the Site is navigable by keyboard</li>
        <li>Writing descriptive alt text for meaningful images</li>
        <li>Testing pages as the Site evolves and addressing issues as they're found</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Known Limitations</h2>
      <p>
        Despite our efforts, some content or features on the Site — including
        embedded videos, third-party tools, or older content — may not yet be
        fully accessible. We are working to address these limitations over
        time.
      </p>

      <h2>Feedback</h2>
      <p>
        If you encounter an accessibility barrier on this Site, please let us
        know. We take reports seriously and will do our best to address the
        issue. Please include the page URL and a description of the problem
        you encountered.
      </p>
      <p>
        Contact: <a href="mailto:mike@mikemurphy.co">mike@mikemurphy.co</a>
      </p>

      <h2>Technical Specifications</h2>
      <p>
        Accessibility on this Site relies on HTML, CSS, and JavaScript, and
        the Site is built with Astro. This statement was created with
        reference to the W3C Web Accessibility Initiative's guidance on
        accessibility statements.
      </p>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
